item.title: By: Amy Graczyk
item.dc:creator: Amy Graczyk
item.description: I'm in awe! So thrilled for you guys! What a hoot.... Maybe we'll catch you near Ft. Meyers beach, my parents live on Marco Island! Or the Graczyks may just need skiing in Colorado next winter. Our kids learned on alpine valley but we can't wait to get them to Colorado. Happy planning!
item.content:encoded:
I’m in awe! So thrilled for you guys! What a hoot…. Maybe we’ll catch you near Ft. Meyers beach, my parents live on Marco Island! Or the Graczyks may just need skiing in Colorado next winter. Our kids learned on alpine valley but we can’t wait to get them to Colorado. Happy planning!
